{"tid":1980370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人想寫信俾還押咗五個月嘅消防手足？","createTime":"2020-04-20T05:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T02:54:33.000Z","uid":40542,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d1fa03329a6e176eaa668003334fd6ee8f1a69b0","tid":1980370,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:06:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">多謝手足，辛苦手足</span></span><br />\n<strong><ins>【向消防員方sir送暖】</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n去年連串反送中行動中，於11月在旺角衝突中不幸被捕的消防員<strong><ins>方志雄(方sir)</ins></strong>，最近被控方修改其控罪為<strong><ins>一項管有物品意圖摧毁財產罪、一項拒捕罪及一項管有違禁武器罪，另加一項非法集結罪共四項控罪</ins></strong>。他早前申請保釋被拒，目前已被還押近半年。<br />\n<br />\n方sir曾參與2017年颱風襲港時在飛鵝山的營救行動，並獲發為消防員最高榮耀的嘉許，足證他守護香港愛護市民之心，惜這次不幸被迫害而遭受還押。<br />\n<br />\n失去自由這五個多月，<strong><ins>方sir 的妻子為他誕下孩子，為人父的他因此從未能擁抱自己的孩子</ins></strong>，初生小寶寶失去父親疼愛的機會，據報<strong><ins>太太亦患上產後抑鬱症</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n本平台收到許多同道對方sir的關心和問候，在取得他的同意下，現幫助收集大家的心意卡和信件。<br />\n<br />\n同道們即日起可留言、私訊或將心意卡和信件寄到本平台信箱：<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">尖沙咀郵箱98697號</span></ins></strong></span>。我們會將大家的關心和問候，一一轉交到方sir手中，希望能讓他知道，很多市民仍不住的關心和惦記他及他的一家。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎仍然在全球肆虐，本平台深盼各位同道忙於抗疫的同時，能夠抽空將關心方sir的心意轉化成訊息或信件，讓我們送到他手中。同道們給予方sir的每一個鼓勵和打氣，將成為他面對四面圍牆時重要的精神支柱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg8-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/94030603_2741940082759773_3270670557145726976_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=2BFwFzbBUtoAX9tcqeO&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg8-1.fna&amp;oh=37dc5ab7ca30d832724f3bd4e01b55d4&amp;oe=5EC48C61\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg8-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F94030603_2741940082759773_3270670557145726976_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D2BFwFzbBUtoAX9tcqeO%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg8-1.fna%26oh%3D37dc5ab7ca30d832724f3bd4e01b55d4%26oe%3D5EC48C61&h=c3e6cee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521/2741940079426440/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1989972677956521%2F2741940079426440%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=d081cf42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521/2741940079426440/</a>"},{"pid":"4a7ea172f4a2673b60ca6c08a34ee2114233b884","tid":1980370,"uid":40542,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"除咗方手足外，啱啱個個禮拜仲有幾位手足被還押/判監，請唔好忘記佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>還押個案</ins></strong><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">林(21)</span></ins></strong> - 管有2支疑似汽油彈 #200413葵涌<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>被判入獄</ins></strong><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">羅(23) - 判監10個月</span></ins></strong> - 管有伸縮棍、摺刀等 #1117尖沙咀 #理大事件<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">莊(64) - 判監5星期</span></ins></strong>(保釋等候上訴) - 拍打🐶嚴潔賢胸口及腳踢🐶戚健暉面部 #0922屯門<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>被判入勞教中心<br />\n</ins></strong>1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">蔡(17)</span></ins></strong> - 管有汽油彈、鐵錘 #1111屯門<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>被判入更生中心</ins></strong><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">梁(20)</span></ins></strong> - 管有汽油彈 #0907旺角"},{"pid":"af8ce2851f8b235fb81efa76574f8c3c06a5f5b5","tid":1980370,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a7ea172f4a2673b60ca6c08a34ee2114233b884","tid":1980370,"uid":40542,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"除咗方手足外，啱啱個個禮拜仲有幾位手足被還押/判監，請唔好忘記佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>還押個案</ins></strong><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">林(21)</span></ins></strong> - 管有2支疑似汽油彈 #200413葵涌<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>被判入獄</ins></strong><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">羅(23) - 判監10個月</span></ins></strong> - 管有伸縮棍、摺刀等 #1117尖沙咀 #理大事件<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">莊(6